name: Kjøttbullar og morraduller
summary: Randi has to swallow many camels to get the family to Harry's shop. Liam never gets peace of mind, and August tries to cut the umbilical cord.

name: Hear No Evil, See No Evil, Say No Evil
Once a Mistake Twice a Habit
WORLD TAG LEAGUE 2020/BEST OF THE SUPER Jr.27 Finals
The Third Candidate
summary: The mysterious murder of a female student causes unrest in university circles. With a close suspect, a close associate and friend, Professor Dimitris Lainis hastens to unravel the mystery.

name: New World Order
summary: Investigations into the murder have begun. And while the new Deputy Chief is determined to change everything, a mysterious file reaches the hands of the Director of Police Laboratories.

name: Daughter of Forkeas
summary: Continuing the search for the murdered student, the police take DNA and fingerprints from the professors and the university staff. The pressure peaks when a new corpse is discovered.

name: Enemies Within Gates
summary: The two victims have one thing in common: a tattoo on Medusa's head. Later, after his visit to the University, Lieutenant Sklavis finds a note with the name of a girl.

name: A New Alliance
summary: Everything shows that the organization continues its activities. And while Christina is doing an interview in prison, the police visit the mother of the murdered student. Is there any new evidence of her death.

name: King Under Threat
summary: A new suitor for the position of the leader of the organization makes his appearance. Meanwhile, police officer Carra continues the investigation, while a creepy video reaches the hands of Velissaratos.

name: The Three Packages
summary: While Lainis learns about the video, journalist Stergiou risks her life again. Meanwhile, the police continue the investigations and the unexpected meeting of two members of the organization brings upset.

name: An Unbearable Victory
summary: All the pieces of the puzzle are in place. All that is missing is the arrest of the culprits and the identification of the Reptile. A voluntary testimony will lead the police to a meeting with him, in the subversive finale.

name: Anushka
summary: Amelia and Pierre arrive in Russia; after a while, things start to go wrong.

name: Could we Have Universal Flu Vaccine?
Day One
summary: Nine teenage girls are en route to Hawaii when their plane fails, leaving them stranded on a remote island. Among them we meet Leah, who has survived to tell their story to a pair of federal investigators. Flashbacks offer an intimate look at Leah's pre-island life, and the taboo relationship that broke her heart.

name: Day Two
summary: The castaways are still reeling after a tragic event. Frustrated by everyone else's inaction, Rachel leads an expedition to the island's summit to get a lay of the land. We learn more about her career as an elite athlete, the extreme measures she's taken to succeed, and the brutal truth that she isn't sharing with the others.

name: Day Three
summary: Leah, Rachel, and Nora swim out to the plane wreckage and return with a crucial find. Fellow Texans Dot and Shelby search for a cave that might provide better shelter, but their contentious relationship makes matters difficult. Flashbacks reveal heart-wrenching secrets about Dot's home life.

name: Day Six
summary: A shelter-building contest turns ugly. Toni provokes strife on her team, and we'll learn in flashback that this isn't the first time her rage issues have caused devastating harm.

name: Day Seven
summary: When one of the castaways goes missing, a search party heads out to find her. We learn more about Fatin's past, which isn't exactly the glamorous thrill ride the others thought it was. At the end of their exhausting day, the girls make a shocking discovery that stokes Leah's doubts about the island.

name: Day Twelve
summary: A sudden illness rips through the beach camp, affecting nearly every castaway. As the girls fight for survival, we learn more about Leah's past and how she's been faring since her rescue.

name: Day Fifteen
summary: A tidal surge forces the castaways to relocate their camp. Still suspicious of the island and how they got there, Leah turns her paranoia on one of the other girls, viciously accusing her of knowing more than she's letting on. In flashback, Jeanette's astonishing backstory is unveiled.

name: Day Sixteen
summary: Assuming that rescue is imminent, the castaways let loose. The only girl who doesn't feel festive is Shelby, and a look into her past reveals why.

name: Day Twenty-Two
summary: Starvation becomes a very real possibility for the weakened girls. Martha could spare them from that fate, but it would require a sacrifice she's not prepared to make. Flashbacks take us into her past, revealing the childhood trauma that's made it hard for Martha to grow up and rise to difficult challenges. Leah's paranoia about the island escalates to a fever pitch.

name: Day Twenty-Three
summary: On the island, Leah feels closer than ever to proving that someone's behind their predicament. Post-rescue, fed up with the tight-lipped authorities, Leah goes searching for her own answers.

name: Chapter 15: The Believer
summary: To move against the Empire, the Mandalorian needs the help of an old enemy.

name: High School Musical: The Musical: The Holiday Special
summary: In this all-new holiday music special, the cast of High School Musical: The Musical: The Series delivers an abundance of feel-good holiday cheer. They perform their favorite Christmas, Hanukkah and New Year's songs and share anecdotes from their memorable holidays, best – and most embarrassing! – presents, favorite holiday traditions, family Christmas photos, and poignant New Year's resolutions. High School Musical: The Musical: The Holiday Special will also feature a sneak peek of the very first performance in the highly anticipated second season of High School Musical: The Musical: The Series.

summary: "I'm not leaving without you!" Our DCPL Friends, can they really get out of this danger?

name: The Brave Little Squire
summary: Mickey dreams of being a knight, but when he is chosen to be Sir Mortimer's squire, he discovers his new boss's heroic reputation is a fairytale.

name: An Ordinary Date
summary: Mickey and Minnie attempt to make their ordinary dinner date into something extraordinary.

name: Feeling Left Out in a Friend Group of Three
TayNew Meal Date Special
summary: TayNew take an extra special meal date to Nakhon Pathom, a night market close to Bangkok where the duo try as many food stalls as they can.

name: Box Cutter
summary: Olivia is on a singular mission to be with Marcus and nothing will stand in her way. She and Wallace follow him - straight into the Piper's lair.

name: En la boca del lobo
summary: Raquel prepares to start her new job as a literature teacher at a high school grappling with intense drama and tragedy.

name: Lo saben
summary: After her privacy is violated and being threatened, Raquel attempts to command respect from her students. Roi opens up to Viruca in his essays.

name: Cuenta hasta tres
summary: A guilt-ridden Raquel must decide how to respond to the blackmail involving her upcoming exam. Iago starts to get to know Viruca outside of class.

name: Caída en picado
summary: Desperate to learn more about Viruca, Raquel dives deeper into the late teacher's life. In the past, Iago is devastated by a realization.

name: El lugar secreto
summary: Raquel's fear of her students increases and she voices her concerns to Germán. Viruca struggles with how to resolve her parents' financial situation.

name: Lo que no quise ver en ti
summary: Raquel continues to unravel a dangerous web of lies as she tries to determine whether she can trust even those closest to her.

name: La tercera víctima
summary: Roi decides to do some investigating of his own. Raquel starts turning to an unlikely source for comfort. Iago continues to seek attention from Viruca.

name: El desorden que dejas
summary: As Raquel gets closer to discovering the truth about Viruca's death, she puts herself in grave danger. Iago makes a torturous decision.

name: Å selge de bæra man har
Bound To Happen
summary: Sometimes, actions speak louder than words. #InfluencersEP4 will show how loud it is.

name: Episode 3
summary: In Soo begins his first day at the recording company, meanwhile Sang Yi is bogged down with administrative work instead of being in the studio.

name: Episode 4
summary: Yoo Jin and In Soo negotiate the details of his recording contract.  One important item arises, Sang Yi as assistant producer will live with In Soo until his debut.

name: #YourHomeNaked
summary: An unfortunate event will bridge two different worlds.

name: I Received a Wedding Invitation From My Ex
Meet the Sobiechs
summary: Intercut with footage from their auditions, we meet Fin, Sabrina, Madison, Neve, and Tom as Justin sends the cast to meet their real-life counterparts in Minnesota and New York City. The group bonds over their love of Zach, and the actors discover inspiration to bring their roles to life.

name: All Aboard the Hot Diggity Dog Express!
"Inside the Hill"
summary: The season finale of Tooning Out The News features Rudy Giuliani's Covid diagnosis, Joe Biden's cabinet picks, and a look back at the wild year of 2020.

name: A Tale of Two Kitties
summary: Alex is mistaken for a Maine Coon and takes over that cat's life in the penthouse. At first, VERY comfortable with his shmancy new life, Alex grows to miss his old life and learns that it's lonely at the top.

name: Fire Marshal Melman
summary: On Junior Marshals' Day at the fire station, Melman gets stuck in a firetruck on its way to a real emergency. With Alex's help, Melman must overcome his fear of heights to help save a stuck cat, and learn that even heroes get scared sometimes.

name: Fancy Fifths
summary: When Marty accidentally "steals" a pair of slippers from a department store, he plans an elaborate "heist" to return them and learns in the end that it's easier to own up to your mistakes than to cover them up.

name: Hedgehog Sitters Club
summary: When a litter of hedgehogs are temporarily relocated to the habitat, Alex, Marty, Melman, and Gloria become their "babysitters."

name: CupKate
summary: It's Kate's birthday and everyone in the habitat has something amazing planned- but Melman's worried that his homemade/hoof-made gift won't measure up.

name: Pest Side Story
summary: Gloria becomes determined to earn her Queen of Kindness Kidizen badge and welcomes some free-spirited rats who need a place to stay into the habitat.

name: Royal Runaway? Ultimate Fate of Duchess Anastasia Revealed
summary: Following the execution of the Russian Tsar and his family in 1918, persistent rumors circulated of his youngest daughter Anastasia's possible escape. Over 100 years later, cutting edge technology finally provides a definitive answer to Anastasia's fate.

name: The Most Wonderful Crime of the Year
summary: When Rachel is put in charge of running Beatz 101's charity Christmas telethon and the starring act's props and costumes are mysteriously destroyed right before the show, Owen takes it upon himself to uncover the "whodunnit" mystery.

name: Episode 9
summary: Amber shares her mom's advice for holiday travel and creates a holiday hotline.
